LibreSportGPS.

This project is a free (libre) software in development state. At this moment it is usable to debug and test it.

It is a GPS program to use in your sport sessions (cycling, running, trekking, mtb, canicross, etc).

Features:
- Data view with information about distance, speed, average speed, etc.
- List of your activities (tracks).
- Activities saved (gpx) in your SD Card.
- Detail of your activities: name, description, sport icon, distance, speed stats, elevation gain, etc.
- Profile of your acitivities.
- Tracks on map view (OpenStreetMap View).
